cpl.readme: Provides an YouTube-inspired Video.js skin for use with the [[TwTube plugin|https://github.com/TheDiveO/TwTube]] created using the [[Videojs Skin Generator|http://www.scriptsmashup.com/Video_Skin_Generator/Videojs/videojs-skin-generator.html]]. Simply install this plugin into your ~TiddlyWiki alongside the ~TwTube plugin and you're done.
